    <title>Women and Girls contributor: William Davies</title>
    <description>Wil Davies has been a journalist and filmmaker for 14 years, working all over the world, from Papua New Guinea to Mongolia to Congo. Previously based in Kenya and Thailand, he now lives in Oxford, England, with his dog, partner and children. You can see more of his work at www.williamdaviesfilms.com and reach him on Twitter @WilwithoneL.
